                            "termAccession": ""
                        },
                        "description": "<p>Following extraction, the samples were filtered and subjected to chip-based nanoelectrospray DI-MS analysis in positive and negative mode using an Advion TriVersa Nanomate combined with a Thermo Scientific Q-Exactive HF high resolution mass spectrometer.</p>",
                        "uri": "",
